<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA27">
<l>aṭiyāṟ paṭikaṭanta muttōva taṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>muṭiyāl vicumpaḷanta muttō neṭiyāy</l>
<l>ceṟikaḻalka ṭāṇimirttuc ceṉṟulaka mellā</l>
<l>maṟikilāmā ṉīyaḷanta vaṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Was it joy that you crossed the earth with [your] foot or, if not that,</l>
<l>was it joy that you measured the sky with [your] crown, long one,</l>
<l>that day you went [and] measured without being able to know,</l>
<l>the whole world, stretching out [your] foot with tight anklets?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
